videos.headline: Snead's 16-yard TD gives East Carolina early lead over Tulsa
videos.description: Holton Ahlers completes a 16-yard pass to Tyler Snead for a touchdown to give East Carolina an early 7-0 lead over Tulsa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Snead's 16-yard TD gives East Carolina early lead over Tulsa) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson cruises to 25-yard East Carolina TD
videos.description: C.J. Johnson swiftly avoids Tulsa defenders as he makes his way 25 yards down the field into the end zone to extend East Carolina's lead to 14-3.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnson cruises to 25-yard East Carolina TD) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith connects with Stokes for 25-yard Tulsa TD
videos.description: Zach Smith finds a wide-open Keylon Stokes who makes his way into the end zone to score a 25-yard Tulsa touchdown and cut the East Carolina lead to 17-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith connects with Stokes for 25-yard Tulsa TD) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Santana escapes multiple defenders for 39-yard Tulsa TD
videos.description: Tulsa takes a 27-23 lead over East Carolina as JuanCarlos Santana slips away from multiple tackles and reaches the end zone to score a 39-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Santana escapes multiple defenders for 39-yard Tulsa TD) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilkerson scores late goal line touchdown for Tulsa lead
videos.description: T.K. Wilkerson leaps into the end zone from the goal line to score a touchdown to give Tulsa a 34-30 lead over East Carolina late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilkerson scores late goal line touchdown for Tulsa lead) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Santana escapes multiple defenders for 39-yard Tulsa TD
videos.description: Tulsa takes a 27-23 lead over East Carolina as JuanCarlos Santana slips away from multiple tackles and reaches the end zone to score a 39-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Santana escapes multiple defenders for 39-yard Tulsa TD) 2020/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris scores go-ahead East Carolina TD
videos.description: Rahjai Harris quickly turns around to make the catch and fall into the end zone as East Carolina retakes the lead 30-27 over Tulsa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris scores go-ahead East Carolina TD) 2020/10/30 ESHEET
